txt.en: 'Gadda and the others left because Sithric is corrupt....'
'I hear he left because Sithric is a murderer!'
'Come, men! Let us join Stanric and [placeholder].'
'Sithric has men looking for you right now! You should run!'
'Why have you returned, friend? It must be urgent, if you are risking so much.'
'I cannot believe Sithric would stoop to such lies to secure his power here!'
'And for what? To starve us out, and cripple us.'
